data.description: Beautifully maintained home in Shadow Moss with NEW roof and water heater is ready for you to enjoy! As you enter the foyer to the living room and dining area you’ll instantly feel at home. Discover an adorable reading nook nestled underneath the staircase. An inviting eat-in kitchen boasts all stainless steel appliances that opens up to the family room with fireplace. Upstairs you’ll find 3 large comfortable bedrooms and a beautiful oversized primary bedroom with tray ceiling and plenty of space for relaxing. Enjoy the breeze on your screened in porch and an outdoor dining area perfect for your backyard summer barbecues.
